data.value:
1. Execute Visual Studio's Command Prompt with elevated privilege.
2. Run: makecert -sk MyCert -ss MY -sr LocalMachine -n CN=mycompany.com -sky exchange -r
3. Obtain thumbprint of certificate using certificate manager e.g. 3228f47d6f0a56c47f62d96b9d0e8580049389a0. ‎ To use PFX file...
4. Create self-signed PVK
makecert -sv mycompany.pvk -n "CN=mycompany.com" mycompany.cer
5. Convert PVK to PFX
PVK2PFX –pvk mycompany.pvk –spc mycompany.cer –pfx mycompany.pfx
